    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Before / In front of",
          "arabic": "قبل / قدام"
        },
        "text": "When describing a location relative to another, you'll hear 'قبل' (qabl) meaning 'before' or 'قدام' (oddam) meaning 'in front of'. 'قدام' is very common for physical location.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "هو قبل البنك.",
            "english": "It's before the bank.",
            "transliteration": "Howa qabl el bank."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "المتحف قدام المستشفى.",
            "english": "The museum is in front of the hospital.",
            "transliteration": "El matḥaf oddam el mostashfa."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "After / Behind",
          "arabic": "بعد / ورا"
        },
        "text": "Similarly, 'بعد' (ba'd) means 'after' and 'ورا' (wara) means 'behind'. 'ورا' is commonly used for physical location. Sometimes you might hear 'ورّا' (warra) which means the same.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "هتلاقيه بعد العمارة.",
            "english": "You'll find it after the building.",
            "transliteration": "Hatla'eeh ba'd el 'emara."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "القسم ورا المتحف.",
            "english": "The police station is behind the museum.",
            "transliteration": "El qism wara el matḥaf."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Beside / Next to",
          "arabic": "جنب"
        },
        "text": "To say 'beside' or 'next to', use 'جنب' (gamb). This is a very useful word for pinpointing locations.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "البنك جنب المستشفى.",
            "english": "The bank is next to the hospital.",
            "transliteration": "El bank gamb el mostashfa."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "المحطة جنب السوق.",
            "english": "The station is beside the market.",
            "transliteration": "El maḥaṭṭa gamb es-soo'."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
